   <head>THE AVTHOR TO HIS BOOKE.</head>
   <l>NOw Farewell Booke, trauell the Word so wide,</l>
   <l>Hauing no Tutor, Truths thy only guide:</l>
   <l>From enuious tongues Truth will still defend thee,</l>
   <l>To good and bad mens Iudgements I commend thee.</l>
